## Bastion Host

A Bastion Host (jump server) provides **secure SSH access to private subnet instances**.

```
Your Laptop
     │  SSH port 22
     ▼
Bastion Host  ← public subnet, Elastic IP
     │  SSH using private IP
     ▼
Private EC2   ← private subnet, no public IP
```

```bash
# Connect to bastion
ssh -i demo.pem ubuntu@<BASTION-PUBLIC-IP>

# From bastion, connect to private instance
ssh -i demo.pem ubuntu@10.0.2.15
```

