## Common Mistakes to Avoid

| Mistake | Fix |
|---|---|
| LB in private subnet | LB must be in **public subnet** |
| EC2 has no public IP but no IGW route | Add IGW route to public subnet route table |
| Forgot to enable DNS hostnames | Enable in VPC settings for public DNS names |
| NAT Gateway in private subnet | NAT Gateway must be in **public subnet** |
| One NAT Gateway for all AZs | Use one NAT Gateway **per AZ** for HA |
| NACL missing return traffic rule | NACL is stateless — allow ephemeral ports 1024-65535 outbound |
| Security group blocking LB to EC2 | EC2 SG must allow port from **LB security group** as source |
| AMI from different region in Launch Template | AMI IDs are **region-specific** |
